{"tid":2445280,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"半山雍景臺第一及第二座與殷樺花園第一及第二期列受限區域","createTime":"2021-03-13T13:29:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T14:00:09.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fe704729e46b4a88bd9d9427530cc9e5269c8ac8","tid":2445280,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:29:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580431-20210313.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580431-20210313.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfDsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=b2709c91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580431-20210313.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=47fc7d26\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580431-20210313.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n政府在港島半山採取圍封強制檢測行動，晚上8時半將羅便臣道雍景臺第一座及第二座，以及殷樺花園第一期及第二期列為「受限區域」，在區域內的人士要留在處所並接受強制檢測，目標是明早約9時完成行動。<br />\n<br />\n當局說，由於雍景臺及殷樺花園近期出現新型肺炎確診個案，經評估後認為相關區域感染風險有機會較高，因此決定採取有關行動。當局又說，明白會為市民帶來不便，已安排在晚上大部分市民回家後開始行動。<br />\n<br />\n大批警員在晚上8時後到場，在殷樺花園對開的羅便臣道馬路設封鎖線並拉起車閘，駛至的車輛要右轉往衛城道離開，有巴士乘客下車步行離開。"},{"pid":"2a06310c2754c1f538601386d8beb97146903c1f","tid":2445280,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:42:56.000Z","msg":"又話唔封半山既"},{"pid":"4e0b3c0efc325bf762292dddd806e0278730a069","tid":2445280,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T14:00:09.000Z","msg":"我返唔到屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}